WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.240
Hi.

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:02.240
Welcome to WakeUpNow.

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:05.649
Today we're going to learn how to use the
new WakeUpNow app for the iPhone.

00:00:05.649 --> 00:00:11.269
After you've downloaded the app, you can launch
the app by touching the WakeUpNow icon.

00:00:11.269 --> 00:00:14.919
Press the "login" button at the top of the
screen.

00:00:14.919 --> 00:00:22.869
Enter your username and password then hit
"login".

00:00:22.869 --> 00:00:27.210
To search for savings in your area, touch
the "Nearby" icon.

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:31.140
The app will automatically recognize your
current location and will display businesses

00:00:31.140 --> 00:00:32.140
in your area.

00:00:32.140 --> 00:00:36.610
Each orange balloon represents a business
that offers savings through WakeUpNow.

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:43.710
To view the deal, simply touch the balloon
and then touch the arrow.

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:57.210
To use the deal, scroll to the bottom and
press "get it now!" and then press "merchant

00:00:57.210 --> 00:00:58.210
redeem".

00:00:58.210 --> 00:01:22.090
To go back 
to the homepage, tap the "Home" button on

00:01:22.090 --> 00:01:23.090
the bottom.

00:01:23.090 --> 00:01:52.789
To view WakeUpNow Daily Deals, touch 
the Daily Deals icon.

00:01:52.789 --> 00:02:00.369
To use the deal, scroll to the bottom and
tap "Get it Now!"

00:02:00.369 --> 00:02:04.499
To read WakeUpNow News, tap the "News" icon
on the home page.

00:02:04.499 --> 00:02:11.470
You will be directed to the WakeUpNow Post.

00:02:11.470 --> 00:02:17.010
Congratulations!

00:02:17.010 --> 00:02:19.190
You're now ready to use the WakeUpNow iPhone
app!

